OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1775127608
OL,3,CTwo people arrested after man's death
OL,5,FTwo people have been arrested after
OL,6,Fthe death of a man in Blackburn.
OL,8,FPolice were called after the man, who
OL,9,Fwas in his 30s, died in hospital on
OL,10,FSaturday 28 March.
OL,12,FThe victim was in an "altercation"
OL,13,Fwith two men outside the Home Bargains
OL,14,Fon Byrom Street at around 6:45pm on
OL,15,FFriday 27 March.
OL,17,FHe later collapsed and was taken to
OL,18,Fhospital, where he died from a head
OL,19,Finjury, a post mortem examination
OL,20,Fconfirmed.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/3
