OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1775127608
OL,3,CTwo people arrested after man's death
OL,5,FTwo men, both in their 40s, were
OL,6,Farrested on suspicion of murder on
OL,7,FTuesday 31 March.
OL,9,FDetective Inspector Pete Macdonald
OL,10,Fsaid: "First and foremost, my thoughts
OL,11,Fare with this man's loved ones at this
OL,12,Fincredibly distressing time.
OL,14,F"Our investigation is very much in its
OL,15,Fearly stages, but we have a dedicated
OL,16,Fteam carrying out enquiries as we try
OL,17,Fto piece together what has happened.
OL,19,F"While we have made two arrests, our
OL,20,Fenquiries are very much ongoing, and
OL,21,Fwe are asking for the public's help.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/3
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
