OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1775127608
OL,3,CTwo people arrested after man's death
OL,5,F"We know from the CCTV we have already
OL,6,Fexamined that there are a number of
OL,7,Fvehicles and witnesses at Home
OL,8,FBargains at the time so we would
OL,9,Freally like to speak to anyone who was
OL,10,Fin the area between 4pm and 9.30pm on
OL,11,FFriday 27th March and who has dashcam
OL,12,Ffootage or mobile footage or who may
OL,13,Fhave been a witness to this incident
OL,14,Fto get in touch."
OL,16,FPolice are appealing for anyone with
OL,17,Finformation to contact them.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/3
